# AI Customer Service Software: 6 Best Solutions for 2024
Looking for AI customer service software? Here is an overview of the top 6 solutions and their features, pricing, and user ratings in 2024.

## Introduction to AI Customer Service
When brands want to understand their customers, they have to communicate with them. Once customers feel engaged, appreciated, and welcomed by support teams, they tend to communicate more, stay in touch, be loyal, and eagerly participate in your marketing campaigns.

## 6 Best AI Customer Service Software Tools
### 1. Chatfuel
* Source: Chatfuel
* Chatfuel is a chatbot development company providing human-like interaction and streamlining customer service operations.
* Features:
	+ Facilitated chatbot creation
	+ Cross-channel messaging
	+ Predictive analytics
	+ Customer knowledge base
	+ Automated instant responses to customer interactions
	+ Streamlined customer service operations
	+ Shared inbox
* Pricing:
	+ Business (Instagram/Facebook): $14.99/month
	+ Business (WhatsApp): $49.49/month
	+ Enterprise: $300/month
* User ratings:
	+ G2: 4.5
	+ Capterra: 4.4

### 2. Zendesk
* Source: Zendesk
* Zendesk is AI customer service software able to provide businesses with advanced generative AI chatbots that anticipate customer needs and actions.
* Features:
	+ Instant reaction to customer queries
	+ Autonomous task execution
	+ Data-driven insights for customer interactions
	+ Easy to customize
* Pricing:
	+ Support Team: $19/month
	+ Suite Team: $55/month
	+ Suite Growth: $89/month
	+ Suite Professional: $115/month
	+ Suite Enterprise: CUSTOM
* User ratings:
	+ G2: 4.3

### 3. Tidio
* Source: Tidio
* Tidio is an AI customer service interaction platform where a natural language processing AI bot (Lyro), email marketing, and live chats work together to tackle support requests and provide the best customer service.
* Features:
	+ Proactive support with live chats
	+ Easy set-up protocol
	+ Smart View for comprehensive analytics
* Pricing:
	+ Free: 50 customer conversations
	+ Starter: $29/month
	+ Growth: $59/month
	+ Tidio +: $749/month
	+ Enterprise: $2999/month
* User ratings:
	+ G2: 4.7

### 4. Kustomer
* Source: Kustomer
* Kustomer is generative AI customer service software that combines AI assistants, emailing and CRM platform functionality.
* Features:
	+ Ready-made templates
	+ Customizable template elements
	+ Self-service customer interaction
	+ Contextual engagement
* Pricing:
	+ Enterprise: $89/month
	+ Ultimate: $139/month
* User ratings:
	+ G2: 4.4

### 5. Custify
* Source: Custify
* Custify is an AI customer service assistant with deep understanding of customer behavior and lifecycles based on enhanced analytics tools.
* Features:
	+ Big data application
	+ Unified customer account
	+ API integration
	+ Powerful dashboards
* Pricing:
	+ Available upon request
* User ratings:
	+ G2: 4.6

### 6. Intercom
* Source: Intercom
* Intercom is among the leading generative artificial intelligence customer service experience tools.
* Features:
	+ AI tools integrations
	+ Maximized automation
	+ Multilingual support
	+ Advanced self-service support
* Pricing:
	+ Essential: $39/month
	+ Advanced: $99/month
	+ Expert: $139/month
* User ratings:
	+ G2: 4.5

## AI Customer Service Software: What to Look for
In addition to key features and pricing data, there are other things worth mentioning while choosing a customer service AI tool for your support team.

### Selection Criteria
* Security
* Scalability
* Integration facilitation
* Customization
* Accuracy of performance

